[doorbell chimes]

00:10:33.529 --> 00:10:36.032
What a surprise.
You didn't even call first.

00:10:36.115 --> 00:10:37.700
When did you get back from the US?

00:10:38.993 --> 00:10:41.371
I came back last weekend.

