00:11:53.192 --> 00:11:54.944
-[chuckles nervously]
-[Kim Wooju chuckles softly]

00:11:55.028 --> 00:11:57.947
I'll get going now
since your sister is here.

00:11:58.031 --> 00:11:59.240
