00:12:19.385 --> 00:12:21.179
[♪ enthralling orchestral music playing]

00:12:24.766 --> 00:12:25.892
[Kim Wooju chuckles awkwardly]

00:12:25.975 --> 00:12:27.268
I'll get going then.

00:12:28.186 --> 00:12:29.729
-[mouthing] You're dead.
-[Kim Wooju] Bye.

00:12:31.564 --> 00:12:32.857
[Sori] Oh, my.

